            "id": 5941601,
            "title": "小米汽車:上海國際車展不會展示YU7",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社16日專訊》小米(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01810:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01810\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01810-HK</a>)汽車副總裁李肖爽在微博發文稱,小米SU7　Ultra、小米SU7全系產品將參展上海國際車展,惟原先預計明年6、7月正式上市的SUV車型「小米YU7」則未見踪影。李肖爽在留言區回應網民直指,沒有YU7,亦稱「別著急,該來的會以最好的狀態來」。(rh)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/5941601",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-16 17:41:00",
            "source": "cnyes",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "id": 5941600,
            "title": "IDC:小米一季度中國手機出貨量稱冠,按年增39.9%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社16日專訊》調研機構IDC發布今年一季度全球手機市場出貨量報告,小米(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01810:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01810\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01810-HK</a>)手機登頂一季度中國市場出貨量第一,按年增速達到39.9%,大幅領先中國市場平均增速3.3%。華為、OPPO、vivo、蘋果分列第二至第五名。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　今年第一季度,小米出貨量達到1330萬台,按年增長39.9%,市場份額18.6%;華為出貨量1290萬台,按年增長10%,市場份額18%;OPPO出貨量為1120萬台,市場份額15.7%;vivo出貨量為1030萬台,市場份額14.4%;蘋果出貨量980萬台,按年減少9%,市場份額13.7%。</p></section><section><p class=\"\">　</p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　報告引述行業分析師指出,一季度小米手機出貨量、增速兩項指標大幅領先行業,體現了小米自去年一季度末發布小米汽車後,品牌勢能強勁,由量變開始質變。同時一季度發布的旗艦手機小米　15Ultra受消費者追捧,銷量創歷史新高。(bi)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/5941600",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-16 17:45:00",
            "source": "cnyes",
            "kind": 1,
